# The cardputer_client/ package now has its own BUILD file with explicit
# py_binary and py_library targets.  MicroPython *.py files are referenced
# as data dependencies (not compiled by host Python), so they no longer
# need to be excluded.
#
# The cardputer_client/proto/ subdirectory remains visible because
# lma_encoder.py is used in host-side test targets.
